<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4000' id='t-4000'>Alright.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5346' id='t-5346'>I'm going to show you a couple of images</span>
