<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='29000' id='t-29000'>Okay. Now on the left you can see
the hand -- that's the big arrow --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='33300' id='t-33300'>and the penis on the right.
