<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='139000' id='t-139000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='143000' id='t-143000'>Sadly -- this is what it said
