<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='151000' id='t-151000'>It's so sad.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='153000' id='t-153000'>(Laughter)</span>
