</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='154101' id='t-154101'>When I was working on the book,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='157000' id='t-157000'>I interviewed a woman
who can think herself to orgasm.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='161000' id='t-161000'>She was part of a study
at Rutgers University.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='164000' id='t-164000'>You've got to love that. Rutgers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='166000' id='t-166000'>So I interviewed her in Oakland,
in a sushi restaurant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='171000' id='t-171000'>And I said, &quot;So, could you
do it right here?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='174000' id='t-174000'>And she said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='175200' id='t-175200'>&quot;Yeah, but you know I'd rather
