</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='179400' id='t-179400'>But afterwards, she was kind enough
to demonstrate on a bench outside.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='183000' id='t-183000'>It was remarkable.
It took about one minute.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='185120' id='t-185120'>And I said to her,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='188000' id='t-188000'>&quot;Are you just doing this all the time?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:22
